text: Abyzovo (, ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Karaidelsky Selsoviet of Karaidelsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 905 as of 2010. There are 34 streets.Улицы села Абызово == Geography == The village is located 2 km from Karaidel. == Ethnicity == The village is inhabited by Russians and Bashkirs. == References == Category:Rural localities in Karaidelsky District
title: Abyzovo, Republic of Bashkortostan
